\begin{document}
}{}$C_B^{combi}$\end{document} are the inhibitory concentrations of the drugs A and B in the combinations and \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{wasysym} 
\usepackage{amsfonts} 
\usepackage{amssymb} 
\usepackage{amsbsy}
\usepackage{upgreek}
\usepackage{mathrsfs}
